I don't have a good
line tool, so I'm

00:03:27.450 --> 00:03:30.240
going to try my best
to draw it nicely--

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:33.860
is going to look
something like that.

00:03:33.860 --> 00:03:34.950
And you just keep going.

00:03:34.950 --> 00:03:36.040
You just keep going.

00:03:36.040 --> 00:03:37.870
You want to do a straight line.

00:03:37.870 --> 00:03:41.940
So it just keeps going on
and on and on like that.

00:03:41.940 --> 00:03:45.752
It just keeps going.

